{"tid":849951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十一黃賓周真係好撚柒鳩煩","createTime":"2018-10-06T05:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T07:12:04.000Z","uid":10277,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cb39ad0f3b630c46de8d5881b9a0efd5b1c1f1","tid":849951,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:52:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 平時已經有好撚柒多大陸旅客<br />\n旺角站十月一 繁忙時間連氣都透唔到<br />\n尖沙嘴又係痴撚柒線<br />\n依排又興深度行 我住鬼咁遠都一堆堆大陸旅客入黎唔知做乜柒鳩 我屋企嗰邊乜柒都無喎！<br />\n如果有任何大陸旅客係會上連登嘅話<br />\n我真係希望你地 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係地鐵站唔好一字排開手拖手行</span><br />\n就算你要臭鳩住你幾個濕勁小朋友<br />\n我真係忍唔住屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申尖沙嘴行去尖東 條路好撚寬咩屌<br />\n四個人手拖手拉開係咪on9？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/06/135251_3940dc3f3a2c5b91c7eca2b11f32e5f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F06%2F135251_3940dc3f3a2c5b91c7eca2b11f32e5f3.png&h=d7fc8aa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"22b75f3ccfe38008100a693844d90819752f37db","tid":849951,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"快撚柒鳩快d走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0013a1a325ca0bc2de57b6c5776d3ff872fa9005","tid":849951,"uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:55:31.000Z","msg":"d細路真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走黎走去嘈住晒仲要搞到人"},{"pid":"fb68e8401f0b36364959b2b7614047bdf8920fcc","tid":849951,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"你係咪搞港獨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded9e146355babb77d3a1cb54351600055a095b6","tid":849951,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0013a1a325ca0bc2de57b6c5776d3ff872fa9005","tid":849951,"uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,